title: The Stomping Land v0.5.6
description:
The Stomping Land V0.5.6

Edit Launch Game.bat and change your name.
to launch the game and connect to the server Kortal's Area server, run Launch Game.bat
warning: server don't save progresssion if restarted (but crash very rarely)

If you stay stuck at the main menu screen when running the game, the server might be offline. Try again a bit later.

to host a server, run Launch Server.bat

if you want to play solo, on the main menu, click Solo

if you have an error message when launching the game, install NDP451-KB2872776-x86-x64-AllOS-ENU.exe
